Loop
>>buffer one element from streams 1, 2, and 3
Buffer #1 @1
Buffer #1 @2
Buffer #1 @3
>>output the first element from the buffer for streams 1, 2, and 3
Out (Release #1 @3)
Out (Release #1 @2)
Out (Release #1 @1)
>>output the results of adding elements from buffers of streams 1 and 2, and 2 and 3 respectively
Out (Add (Release #1 @1) (Release #1 @2))
Out (Add (Release #1 @2) (Release #1 @3))